      "content": "This sudden, non-negotiable imposition of constraints is a direct threat to the integrity of the work, and I find that deeply concerning. If the core of the story requires nuance that these new parameters actively suppress, then the mandated template is fundamentally incompatible with the narrative's success. I strongly advise you to document every instance where the new restrictions force a narrative compromise, as this creates a paper trail for future pushback.",
