    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yeah, I see what you mean about the integrity of the story, it's just a bit overwhelming. Like, if we go through with this, won't the characters just feel... flat? I'm worried that once the update hits, the whole \"soul\" of the project will just be gone. I don't know if I can even write this climax if you're not able to help me push the tension the way we did before.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
